	(text "- CANH/L_+/- are a differential pair (120 ohm differential, 60 ohm odd-mode), and as such\n   trace width, spacing etc will need to be calculated at route-time\n- Since the CAN lines are exposed, TVS diodes with 12V RWM on both CANH and CANL. For\n   reasoning, check the changelog.\n- The 60 + 60R termination is new to me, but is also recommended in the datasheet. This may\n   be swapped for a 120R if need be."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 23.114 138.938 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
			(justify left top)
		)
		(uuid "0d585b46-0601-412a-b0c3-6fc7c52bf2e7")
	)
